abilities.name: Psystrike
abilities.description: Has a chance to lower the opponent's Special Defense.

abilities.name: Force. Psychic
abilities.description: Adds 1 to the priority of attacks with 100% or greater accuracy that beat opponents with or have Dark Alexander against them.

abilities.name: Insulating Seal
abilities.description: Prevents the opponent from making contact with or landing critical hits with the attack as a result of the foe gaining or moving into the coils.
